data.description:
Welcome home to this East Palestine beauty, where timeless elegance meets modern convenience. This stunning early 1900's architectural gem boasts beautiful hardwood floors, tall ceilings, and an abundance of natural light that fills every room. The spacious backyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings and offers endless possibilities for your personal oasis.

Step inside and be greeted by a large living area that leads to your formal dining room and updated kitchen. Three spacious bedrooms, each offering a serene retreat from the outside world. Need additional space for your hobbies or a home office? No problem! This home also features a bonus room that can be customized to suit your needs.

But it doesn't stop there. Imagine the convenience of a two-car detached garage, ensuring plenty of room for parking and storage. The basement walks out to the yard as well for even more storage opportunities. No need to worry about major updates either - this home has been cared for well with new windows, a new roof, and a new furnace and AC system.

Your safety and peace of mind are our top priorities. That's why we've taken care of the electrical system as well, ensuring it is up to date with the latest standards.

Don't miss the opportunity to own this remarkable piece of history combined with modern comfort. Call today for your showing!
